<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; }
      .credentials { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; }
      .brand { font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to <span class="brand">anatomical.</span></h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi <%= @user.email %>!</h2>

        <p>Your personal trainer <strong><%= @trainer.name %></strong> has added you to <span class="brand">anatomical.</span>, our workout tracking and recovery management platform.</p>

        <div class="credentials">
          <h3>Your Login Credentials</h3>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
          <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <code><%= @temporary_password %></code></p>
        </div>

        <p>Please log in and change your password as soon as possible for security.</p>

        <a href="<%= @login_url %>" class="button">Log In to <span class="brand">anatomical.</span></a>

        <h3>What's Next?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Log in with your credentials above</li>
          <li>Change your password in your profile</li>
          <li>Your trainer will help set up your first split plan</li>
          <li>Start tracking your workouts and recovery</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions, reach out to your trainer <strong><%= @trainer.name %></strong> directly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p><span class="brand">anatomical.</span> - Professional Workout Tracking</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
